<paragraph blockId="7.[264,1324,284,1190]" pageId="7" pageNumber="52">
<emphasis box="[312,401,1044,1069]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="52">Habitat</emphasis>
: From the rich material collected in the 
<collectingRegion box="[880,1119,1044,1070]" country="Iran" name="Khorasan-e Shomali" pageId="7" pageNumber="52">Khorassan Province</collectingRegion>
, we can consider that this species preferably inhabits first order streams, often those with considerably exposure to sunlight, but is restricted to areas with permanent flow.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="7.[264,1324,284,1190]" box="[312,1267,1164,1190]" pageId="7" pageNumber="52">
